# mvm's test loader returns a single compilation unit, so for a package with
# both internal (package log) and external (package log_test) test files it
# keeps the internal ones and drops the external. log's examples
# (ExampleLogger, ExampleLogger_Output) live in the external example_test.go and
# exercise log's runtime.Caller-derived file:line -- the reason log is
# interpreted at all -- so drop the internal log_test.go to let the examples run
# (matching the historical bridged behavior, which served only external tests).
log_test.go
